      "actionDate": "2026-04-02",
      "actionDesc": "Reported to House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Benton MacKaye National Scenic Trail Feasibility Study Act of 2026</strong></p><p>This bill requires the Department of Agriculture to study the feasibility of designating the Benton&nbsp;MacKaye Trail (located in Georgia, Tennessee, and North Carolina) as a national scenic trail.</p>",
